Ghost Field Detail

elementType

public Class elementType
The (more specific) type of our elements (set by the user of the object to state what is allowed to be added to the collection, and hence what is guaranteed to be retrieved from the collection). It is not adjusted based on the content of the collection.

Specifications: instance
